## Data Source:
I used Kaggle to find the dataset.
* https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/trolukovich/football-players-salaries?resource=download

## Data Preperation/Cleaning:
* Remove rows that have value 0 for age, total value, avg year, total guaranteed, fully guaranteed.


## Assumptions:
* Assumed that this data set was from 6 years ago.
